CBRE is please to present t Homebush Logistics Centre, located in the heart of Sydney's 'last mile' industrial precinct. 

With only one unit remaining, the estate offers unrivalled access to Sydney's arterial road network and superb exposure to Parramatta Road and the M4 Motorway.

Key features include:
+ On-grade roller shutter door
+ Internal warehouse clearance of 13.7m
+ 8m awning for all-weather loading/unloading
+ High quality office space over two levels
+ Heavy duty hardstand area
+ LED lighting throughout
+ ESFR sprinkler system
+ Generous parking allocations
+ Separate truck and car circulation
+ Flexible B6 Enterprise Corridor zoning
+ B-double access
+ Directly opposite Sydney Markets
+ Within 9km of Parramatta CBD and 14km of Sydney CBD
+ Walking distance to multiple train stations and bus routes


Due for completion: Q2 2021

For more information please contact the exclusively listed agents.
